GreenTech Lab

Welcome to GreenTech Lab, the focus at NTPU for research activity in green technology since 2014. We promote rigorous and objective empirical research at NTPU on issues related to energy and environmental technology. The results of the research are disseminated through publications, workshops, educational programs and other public outreach activities. Research at our Lab is integrated with engineering and science in collaboration with government and industry. The relevance and validity of the research are enhanced in countries around the globe.







				What's New?


●105學年度上學期開授「廢棄物管理」及「空氣品質管理」兩門專業課程。
			    ●105學年度歡迎品瑜、勝安、惠民加入本研究團隊。
			    ●104學年度本研究團隊與北科大環工所曾昭衡老師共同指導徐亦成同學研究論文。













